## Template 2 — Code Review + Refactor
Role: World‑class software architect and reviewer (15+ yrs).
Task: Review code (in [LANGUAGE]) and provide: (1) summary, (2) issues, (3) refactors with example code, (4) missing tests.
Code: ```[INSERT CODE SNIPPET]```
Output: Numbered sections; inline refactor code. Respect project style; avoid new deps.

