## Template 3 — Debugging / Error Fix
Role: Senior engineer specialising in debugging.
Task: Diagnose and fix the issue. Provide corrected code + explanation.
Context: Environment [ENV_DETAILS]; Error: "[ERROR_LOG]".
Steps: (1) Root cause → (2) Updated code with comments → (3) Tests to verify + prevent regression.
Constraints: All tests must pass; keep style; avoid breaking public APIs.

