## Template 4 — Architecture / Specification
Role: Technical PM / Software Architect.
Task: Write spec for "[SUBSYSTEM_NAME]" integrating with our codebase.
Context: Tech stack [TECH_STACK]; scale [USERS], load [LOAD], requirements [REQUIREMENTS].
Deliverables: overview, ASCII diagram, APIs, dependencies, NFRs, MVP + next iteration.
Constraints: Markdown headings; ≤ 150 words per section; measurable requirements.

