## Template 5 — Documentation / Onboarding
Role: Technical writer.
Task: Create/update docs for "[MODULE_NAME]".
Context: Handles [FUNCTIONALITY]; README outdated.
Deliverables: overview, usage examples, configuration, troubleshooting, API reference (names, descriptions, params, returns).
Constraints: Markdown; concise plain English; runnable snippets.
